<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<h2 id="head-d8baf8fd782413d654510fb0481ec2c17e89be88"><a href="#bottom"><img src="./wiki/starshine/img/moin-bottom.png" alt="[BOTTOM]" height="10" width="14"></a><a href="#top"><img src="./wiki/starshine/img/moin-top.png" alt="[TOP]" height="10" width="14"></a>Coldfire</h2>
<p>
I (<a href="./NerdanelVampire">NerdanelVampire</a>) gave this module idea some serious thought, but decided to go with <a href="./Modules_2fZothiqband">Modules/Zothiqband</a> instad. Anyone is free to implement and improve on this. 
</p>
<h3 id="head-70c07ec18ef89c5309bbb0937f3a6342411e1fdd"><a href="#bottom"><img src="./wiki/starshine/img/moin-bottom.png" alt="[BOTTOM]" height="10" width="14"></a><a href="#top"><img src="./wiki/starshine/img/moin-top.png" alt="[TOP]" height="10" width="14"></a>World</h3>
<p>
The game takes place on an alien world called Erna. Human settlers arrived here several centuries previously, only to be surprised by Erna's unusual properties. The humans were almost destroyed and lost most of their technology, which they have only recently started to recover. But they have also discovered magic and the powers of various godlings. Erna is a place where the world can respond to thoughts and beliefs, up to and including creating gods for one to worship. 
</p>
<p>
Weapons are mainly medieval. Firearms exist, but they are unreliable, and may blow up unless you control your subconscious. (There could be a skill for this.) 
</p>
<h3 id="head-9af3f864702b18442f886c277dd5608a4b2c8795"><a href="#bottom"><img src="./wiki/starshine/img/moin-bottom.png" alt="[BOTTOM]" height="10" width="14"></a><a href="#top"><img src="./wiki/starshine/img/moin-top.png" alt="[TOP]" height="10" width="14"></a>Races</h3>
<p>
Humans 
</p>

    <ul>

    <li>
<p>
 East (good with magic and magic items) 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 West (good with technology) 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 Adept (innate see invisible, good at magic, low sanity) 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 Terata 
</p>
</li>

    </ul>


<p>
Rakh (natives of Erna) 
</p>

    <ul>

    <li>
<p>
 East (barbaric with good stats and stealth) 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 West (better skills) 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 Dark One (psychic vampires) 
</p>
</li>

    </ul>


<p>
Faeborn 
</p>

    <ul>

    <li>
<p>
